These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, sudoku
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, light-blue
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, pop
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, apricot
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, skiing
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, aristoff
1. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is on the far right##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is the person eating apricot##1
5. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | fanta     | cola       |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | sudoku     |
| Color           | orange | light-blue   |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | salsa  |
| Food   | apricot | eggplant |
| Sport           | badminton      | skiing     |
| Cigar     | aristoff    | montecristo   |

