.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, superhero
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, august
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, blood-red
House: craftsman, townhouse
2 different pets are kept: lizard, mouse
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, carrot
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the owner of the mouse is the person eating carrot##1
3. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
4. the townhouse house is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre         | superhero        | horror  |
| Birthday           | june | august  |
| Color   | blood-red            | fuchsia    |
| House   | craftsman     | townhouse   |
| Pet           | lizard         | mouse    |
| Food     | raspberry           | carrot      |

