2. the wooden house is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the dannemann-smoker##1
4. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the tower house##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| House         | tower  | wooden    |
| Food           | asparagus       | pineapple    |
